	<solution id="id6315285">
	  <para id="sol_1">
	    In order to calculate the Fourier transform, all we need
	    to use is <link target-id="eqn1" strength="3"/>, <link document="m10060">complex exponentials</link>,
	    and basic calculus.
	    
	    <equation id="sol1a">
	      <m:math>
		<m:apply>
		  <m:eq/>
		  <m:apply>
